Second Department,

November, 1956

(November 13, 1956)* In the Matter of Seaberg Elevator Co., Inc., Petitioner, against Louis L. Friedman, Justice of the Supreme Court, State of New York, County of Kings, Respondent.

Not published with other decisions of Hov. 13, 1956, 2 A D 2d 892 and Feb. 11, 1957, 3 A D 2d 714. — [Rep.

Application to dismiss petition granted, with $25 costs and disbursements. Present — Nolan, P. J., Wenzel, Beldock, Murphy and Hallinan, JJ.
